<p>可以用前向算法解决</p>
<h2 id="theorem-3-3-1-wspt" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#theorem-3-3-1-wspt"><span>Theorem 3.3.1.(WSPT)</span></a></h2>
<p>前向算法，工作排序按照工期长短：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>d</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>≤</mo><mi>d</mi><mn>2</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mo>≤</mo><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
